resources.string: Recommendations for people to contact based on your message history
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `cidade` ( `codigo` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `nome` VARCHAR(50) NULL DEFAULT NULL, `idEstado` INT(11) NULL DEFAULT NULL);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `endereco` ( `id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `endereco` LONGTEXT NULL, `bairro` LONGTEXT NULL, `cidade` LONGTEXT NULL, `uf` LONGTEXT NULL);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `estado` ( `codigo` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `nome` VARCHAR(50) NULL DEFAULT NULL, `sigla` VARCHAR(50) NULL DEFAULT NULL, `pais` VARCHAR(50) NULL DEFAULT NULL);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `user_decision_attributes` ( `information` varchar ( 45 ), `state` integer, `user_decision_attributes_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `user_decision_id` integer NOT NULL, `data_attribute_id` integer NOT NULL, `anonymised_information` varchar ( 45 ), FOREIGN KEY(`user_decision_id`) REFERENCES `user_decision`(`user_decision_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION, FOREIGN KEY(`data_attribute_id`) REFERENCES `data_attributes`(`data_attributes_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION );

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `request` ( `inferred_decision_id` integer, `uuid` varchar ( 100 ), `user_decision_id` integer, `data_id` integer NOT NULL, `reason` varchar ( 100 ), `consumer_id` integer NOT NULL, `state` integer, `location` varchar ( 45 ), `request_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `check_user` integer, `user_benefit` varchar ( 45 ), `anonymised_information` varchar ( 45 ), FOREIGN KEY(`data_id`) REFERENCES `data`(`data_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION, FOREIGN KEY(`consumer_id`) REFERENCES `consumer`(`consumer_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION, FOREIGN KEY(`user_decision_id`) REFERENCES `user_decision`(`user_decision_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION, FOREIGN KEY(`inferred_decision_id`) REFERENCES `inferred_decision`(`inferred_decision_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION );

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `inferred_decision_attributes` ( `data_attributes_id` integer NOT NULL, `inferred_decision_attributes_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `trust_level` varchar, `inferred_decision_id` integer NOT NULL, `state` integer, `anonymised_information` varchar, FOREIGN KEY(`data_attributes_id`) REFERENCES `data_attributes`(`data_attributes_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION, FOREIGN KEY(`inferred_decision_id`) REFERENCES `inferred_decision`(`inferred_decision_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION );

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `data_attributes` ( `data_id` integer NOT NULL, `attribute` varchar ( 45 ), `inferred` integer, `shared` integer, `data_attributes_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `retention` varchar ( 45 ), `training_set_id`integer, FOREIGN KEY(`data_id`) REFERENCES `data`(`data_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION, FOREIGN KEY (`training_set_id`) REFERENCES `training_set` (`training_set_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION );

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `consumer_attributes` ( `attribute` varchar ( 45 ), `value` varchar ( 45 ), `consumer_attributes_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `consumer_id` integer NOT NULL, FOREIGN KEY(`consumer_id`) REFERENCES `consumer`(`consumer_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION );

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `training_set` ( `training_set_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `device_type` integer, `data_type` varchar ( 45 ), `user_benefit` varchar ( 45 ), `retention` varchar ( 45 ), `location` varchar ( 45 ), `shared` varchar ( 45 ), `inferred` varchar ( 45 ), `result` varchar ( 45 ));
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mlp_models` ( `mlp_models_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `model` BLOB(1024), `template_header` TEXT);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `things` ( `things_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `attribute` VARCHAR(45) , `value` VARCHAR(45));

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `settings` ( `configuration_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `confidence_level`integer , `always_notify` integer , `notify_new_consumer` integer , `sound_notification` integer, `timestamp` DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `training_scenarios` ( `training_scenarios_id` INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `scenario` VARCHAR(255), `state` INTEGER, `decision` INTEGER, `training_set_id` integer, FOREIGN KEY(`training_set_id`) REFERENCES `training_set`(`training_set_id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION);
